{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"60932-dance-mihlali","title":"Dance, Mihlali!","description":"The day of the concert is approaching, and Mihlali is getting more and more nervous. Will she ever be ready to dance in front of all those people?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Matona Fatman"],"illustrators":["Aimee  Ayres"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Book Dash","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/60932-dance-mihlali"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130507/size3/abbca912f758719547f7dc1afe9eac68.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130507/size6/abbca912f758719547f7dc1afe9eac68.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129012/size6/d8c50f8c24d44b23c72115146f4c9cfb.jpg","text":"It is almost time for the big concert at school.\nAll the children are having fun practising.\nBut not Mihlali …","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129015/size6/41bc65d10d796205c6c2f5482b4ef816.jpg","text":"She is worried she will forget her dance steps.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129016/size6/7522be2d78d9173766c7c3fc02db0abc.jpg","text":"“I’ll help you practise at home.”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129017/size6/5aeec02ef1de0810068cce6edac068c9.jpg","text":"“I wish this concert would never happen!”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129020/size6/dda6a93a285f0c744c896487dfca1b39.jpg","text":"Not a chance! The day of the concert is getting closer…","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129023/size6/35ccac1d49159b9dd3a4b26a73a6bb37.jpg","text":"“Granny has sent you a gift.”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129026/size6/6de65386513c86d083eee5f3853cb037.jpg","text":"Mihlali is too worried about the concert to open gifts.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129028/size6/d835f7e62c370019b26627071b48bfed.jpg","text":"Perhaps she should take a look inside.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129031/size6/5cb984470407c78119ad661c4dd0c6c3.jpg","text":"What great dancing shoes from Granny!","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129034/size6/98301f2ad332fbd6057d936c222e6468.jpg","text":"Granny was the\nbest dancer ever.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129036/size6/9b2a464facb6ffbe3b33de77d18e1bc2.jpg","text":"Mihlali practises and practises at school…","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129038/size6/5735ef45ab4084a77d1eeacd5a1ae760.jpg","text":"And at home! \nAnd she dances in her dreams.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129051/size6/7aa99f89183d70f13f138d855f91a533.jpg","text":"Mihlali must rest.\nThe big concert is tomorrow.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129052/size6/4f28e77b32fbf6f582f915c123a77767.jpg","text":"It’s concert day. Mihlali does her dance just right. What great fun! \nAnd surprise! Granny has even come to watch Mihlali dance.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129053/size6/149f9b063bf22c00ec6747e19c2bd1af.jpg","text":"“I danced just like you, Granny.”","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129054/size6/08e4781dc392a19dd020b698dfcbae3d.jpg","text":"“You were amazing!\nYou are the best dancer I’ve ever seen.”","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129055/size6/1e503049b7edec15fa298bf5e92cd948.jpg","text":"18/19","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129056/size6/081c719fefca4c77648cc6cbaf1cde9d.jpg","text":"19/19","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":18,"words":153}}